# ── Source data + build scripts: kept LOCAL, not committed ──────────────────
# Only the GENERATED data/*.json (and the site) ship to the public repo — the same
# way ichinichi-ichigo commits its dataset but not the raw notes it was built from.
#
# Consequence: the source CSVs and the build are NOT in the repo, so data/ can't be
# rebuilt from a fresh clone. Keep your own backup of tools/.
tools/

# ── OS / editor cruft ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log

# ── Node (zero-dependency today, but just in case) ──────────────────────────
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
